n.doxia:doxia-core:1.8 -Djava.io.tmpdir=/path/with/free/space/tmp\n```\n\nBut the current error is definitively `No space left on device`, not a Doxia API/test issue.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_05f384656a294804016a03170f6d748194a8002e4f358d22d4\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 14990, "output": 795, "cacheRead": 43520, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 59305, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1778587389223, "responseId": "resp_05f384656a294804016a0316fee97c81949fd0cc3e6b859f81"}, "toolResults": []}
